Nad's Natural Sugar Wax

Sue Ismiel & Daughters

About Us: Before Nad’s was created back in 1992, no one ever talked about unwanted hair. That first pot of Nad’s Natural Hair Removal Gel changed everything. Today, Nad’s - led by founder Sue Ismiel and her daughters - is renowned as the hair removal innovator, with products tailored, tested and proven to solve the real problem of unwanted hair for women and men around the world.

The no-heat natural wax to silky smooth hair-free skin

Natural Sugar Wax

Using only a few carefully selected natural ingredients, we have created a fast, effective, and gentle sugar wax that helps solve all your body hair removal needs.

Nad’s Hair Removal Natural Sugar Wax warms with body heat as it’s smoothed onto the skin and waxed away – along with your unwanted hair – to leave the skin salon smooth for up to eight weeks. The mistake-proof formula easily washes away with water giving you the confidence to achieve salon results at home.

  • Gentle & natural wax formula suitable for all skin types
  • Ideal for body, legs, arms, bikini, underarms, and face
  • Smooth salon results of up to 8 weeks
  • No heating required - The wax melts with your body heat
  • Wax with confidence - Wax easily washes away with water
Read more

How to use Nad's Natural Sugar Wax

Prep the area to be treated

Wash your hands. Thoroughly clean the area to be treated using the Nad's Pre-Wax Cleansing Soap. Ensure all oils, makeup and moisturisers are removed and then wipe skin completely dry.

Hair should be between 3 to 5 mm long for best results.

Apply the sugarl wax

Apply a thin layer of wax in the direction of hair growth. Coat the spatula with a good portion of wax and slowly apply a thin and even layer in the direction of hair growth.

Tip: If the environment is cold or the wax is too thick, heat in the microwave for 5 - 10 seconds.

Place the cotton strip

Immediately place strip over the wax. Using the palm of your hand firmly smooth over the strip 3-4 times in direction of hair growth.

Remove the strip

Holding skin taut with one hand, quickly pull strip off in the opposite direction of hair growth. The quicker you pull the strip back the more effective the hair removal. Remember to hold skin taut with the other hand and to pull close to the skin rather than away from the skin.

All done. Enjoy up to 8 weeks of silky smooth skin.

Important information

Indications
Hair Removal Epilation

Ingredients
Sucrose, Aqua (Water), Phoenix dactylifera (Date) fruit extract, Mel (Honey), Acetum (Vinegar), Citrus limon (Lemon) juice, Caprylic/Capric triglyceride, Citric acid

Directions
Wash your hands. Thoroughly clean the area to be treated using the Nad's Pre-Wax Cleansing Soap. Ensure all oils, makeup and moisturisers are removed and then wipe skin completely dry. Apply a thin layer of wax in the direction of hair growth. Hair should be at least 3-5mm (1/8 - 1/4 inches)long. Immediately place strip over the wax. Using the palm of your hand firmly smooth over the strip 3-4 times in direction of hair growth. Holding skin taut with one hand, quickly pull strip off in the opposite direction of hair growth. The quicker you pull the strip back the more effective the hair removal. Remember to hold skin taut with the other hand and to pull close to the skin rather than away from the skin.
